  "response": "Okay, here are the Spanish lyrics to the \"La Biblioteca\" rap from Community, as performed by Troy (Donald Glover) and Abed (Danny Pudi), along with a translation and some notes:\n\n**Lyrics:**\n\n**Troy:**\n> E Pluribus Anus, E Pluribus Anus\n\n**Abed:**\n> La biblioteca es mi casa.\n> Yo soy muy contenta.\n> Estoy en la biblioteca\n> Yummy, yummy, me gusta.\n\n**Troy:**\n> E Pluribus Anus, E Pluribus Anus\n\n**Abed:**\n> La biblioteca es muy grande\n> Y todos los libros son gratis.\n> No tengo mucho dinero.\n> La biblioteca es para mi.\n\n**Troy:**\n> E Pluribus Anus, E Pluribus Anus\n\n**Abed:**\n> La biblioteca es muy divertida\n> porque no tengo amigos.\n> la biblioteca es para todos\n> todos mis enemigos.\n\n**Translation:**\n\n**Troy:**\n> E Pluribus Anus, E Pluribus Anus (Out of many, anus - a fictional Greendale motto)\n\n**Abed:**\n> The library is my house.\n> I am very happy.\n> I am in the library\n> Yummy, yummy, I like it.\n\n**Troy:**\n> E Pluribus Anus, E Pluribus Anus\n\n**Abed:**\n> The library is very big\n> And all the books are free.\n> I don't have much money.\n> The library is for me.\n\n**Troy:**\n> E Pluribus Anus, E Pluribus Anus\n\n**Abed:**\n> The library is very fun\n> because I don't have friends.\n> The library is for everyone\n> All my enemies.\n",
